<item>
            <title>[FLINK-4171] StatsD does not accept metrics whose name contains &quot;:&quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-4171</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;StatsDReporter&lt;/tt&gt; mustn&apos;t send metrics whose name contains a &quot;:&quot; character to &lt;tt&gt;StatsD&lt;/tt&gt; because these reports are discarded. The reason is that &quot;:&quot; is used to separate the value from the metric name.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I propose to check the metric names and replace all &quot;:&quot; by a &quot;-&quot; character.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
