                            <comment id="15366093" author="githubbot" created="Thu, 7 Jul 2016 13:31:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user tillrohrmann opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/2212&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/2212&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-4171&quot; title=&quot;StatsD does not accept metrics whose name contains &amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-4171&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-4171&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;metrics&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Replace : chars in StatsD metric names&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    The StatsD server rejects metrics whose names contain the : character. Therefore,&lt;br/&gt;
    metric names which contain : chars will be altered so that : is replaced by -.&lt;/p&gt;

